data.description: Beautiful home thewith 4 bedroom, and 2 baths, with a large patio and fence!!! This property is one of the most desired floor plans, The Cali Model, it will be perfect for a family. The home has granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The home is located approximately 12 minutes from the medical city of Lake Nona, with a plenty of shopping and dining options along Narcoossee Rd. Easy access to 417 and 528. This lovely property has open space, kitchen, dining and living room.  Theres also a Master suite with walk-in closet and 3 large bedrooms, solar panels and a double garage. Don't miss this opportunity!!
